    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏描述：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为幻想世界的英雄，阻止怪物入侵！<strong>《防御遗产》</strong>结合了创新的横向卷轴动作和卡组构建元素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上冒险旅程，招募盟友，并从危险的敌人中保卫自己！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096620/extras/dcce87a67bc42555a09b99c41fa8a985.poster.avif?t=1765314779\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096620/extras/dcce87a67bc42555a09b99c41fa8a985.webm?t=1765314779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096620/extras/dcce87a67bc42555a09b99c41fa8a985.mp4?t=1765314779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>横向卷轴动作：体验激烈的战斗，享受惊人的2D图形和直观的操作。感受抵御成群怪物的快感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡组构建策略：收集各种卡牌，创建独特的卡组。每张卡牌都包含强大的技能，需进行策略性的玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幻想怪物：面对各种只能想象的幻想怪物。与具有不同能力的怪物战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096620/extras/28a868d1f6f5b6a21c0fef67ebe5a40e.poster.avif?t=1765314779\" width=600 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096620/extras/28a868d1f6f5b6a21c0fef67ebe5a40e.webm?t=1765314779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096620/extras/28a868d1f6f5b6a21c0fef67ebe5a40e.mp4?t=1765314779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>技能升级：通过战斗获得经验，升级英雄技能。使用强大的技能有效清除怪物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096620/extras/9c7e4fa42764a857fee9606d893315ad.poster.avif?t=1765314779\" width=600 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096620/extras/9c7e4fa42764a857fee9606d893315ad.webm?t=1765314779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096620/extras/9c7e4fa42764a857fee9606d893315ad.mp4?t=1765314779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>抵御来袭的怪物。选择卡牌使用技能击败敌人。战略性卡组构建是胜利的关键。清除每个关卡，面对越来越强大的怪物，最终击败最终BOSS！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >测试你的策略和技能。准备好成为勇敢的英雄，拯救幻想世界了吗？</p>",
